Subject: Re: [T2] Speaking of CV joints, how do you get them back on??

Courtney Hook wrote:
> seems!! What's the trick?


I hold mine together with zip ties until I'm ready to attach that end. 
I'll put two or three ties on each CV joint through the bolt holes.  Cut 
them off and install on end leaving the other zip tied until you're 
ready to install it.

Good luck!
